title: Independent Candidate Rajab Ali Khan Abbasi wins PK-43 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent Candidate Rajab Ali Khan Abbasi has won the Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly election from PK-43, Abbottabad-II by securing 41,242 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was an Independent candidate Muhammad Javed Abbasi who bagged 20,869 votes.
Overall voters turn-out remained 45.54 per cent.
